description: This file is a React component for a web page that displays a dashboard for managing connectors. It includes UI elements such as buttons, links, and sections for different connectors like Jira and Confluence, and handles fetching and displaying connector data.

methods.name: Home
methods.description: Main React component rendering the dashboard page, managing state and rendering UI elements.

methods.name: OAuthButton
methods.description: Component rendering a button to initiate OAuth login flow for a connector.

methods.name: DisconnectButton
methods.description: Component rendering a button to disconnect a specified connector.

methods.name: CreateJiraIssueButton
methods.description: Component rendering a button to create a Jira issue via API.

methods.name: CreateConfluencePageButton
methods.description: Component rendering a button to create a Confluence page via API.
